ough leader so that she can not only lead her team but protect them as they grow to become fearsome shinobi. She has also shown she has a very poor grasp at the concept of humor as her sense of humor is that she makes poses of sea creatures such as crabs, shrimp, etc. while saying the name of the creature she is doing, even using her swords for the pose.}}

